caption.rendered: ONU indicó que, en los últimos tres años, la violencia de los colonos y las restricciones provocaron el desplazamiento de palestinos en 85 comunidades y zonas de Cisjordania. Foto Referencial / EFE

image_meta.caption: JENIN (-), 23/12/2025.- Israeli soldiers are seen at the evacuated Israeli settlement of Sanur, near the West Bank city of Jenin, 23 December 2025. Israel's security cabinet on 21 December approved the establishment of 19 new settlements in the West Bank, a move described by the finance minister as aimed at preventing the establishment of a Palestinian state. Sanur is one of four settlements in the northern West Bank that were evacuated in 2005, when the government of Ariel Sharon withdrew from the Gaza Strip and from four West Bank settlements. (Yenín) EFE/EPA/ALAA BADARNEH
